{"type": "article", "id": 26291, "title": "水耕智能菜园", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-03T06:50:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 86, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702140241rAcLeDlwWdIz7OnB.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">日本的 Cestec 公司推出的这款名为 Foop 的水耕工作台是一个有着未来感的智能小菜园。Foop 内可以种植各类不高于 25 厘米的蔬菜，将种子和海绵放进栽培杯中，加入水和肥料耐心等待即可。通过配套的 app 你可以随时了解蔬菜的状态，比如还有几天成熟、是否还需要加水等。它的售价为 38800 日元，限量 100 台的首批预订已经截止，你可以通过它的<a href=\"https://foop.cestec.jp/\">官方网站</a>了解更多信息。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140239s0O8mUx4FJXbBq36.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.57375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140240rszNCkmYLeB1AF83.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021402405oUZWcGS472FHP3w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140241YGBtgflzQ14vmIku.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}